OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775056271
OL,3,CUrgent calls to upgrade one of the
OL,4,Cworld's smallest working jails
OL,6,FThe detention centre has historically
OL,7,Fonly been used once or twice a year,
OL,8,Fusually after drink-related incidents
OL,9,F- a toilet was only installed in 2009.
OL,11,FConstables in Sark want to introduce
OL,12,Fpre-fabricated pods for holding cells
OL,13,Finstead, which are already used by
OL,14,Fsome UK local authorities.
OL,16,FThey hope the new facility could be up
OL,17,Fand running by mid-summer, if approved.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
