FL,384,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775056271
OL,3,CUrgent calls to upgrade one of the
OL,4,Cworld's smallest working jails
OL,6,FThe Constables say they have become
OL,7,Fincreasingly reliant on Guernsey
OL,8,FPolice for support - particularly when
OL,9,Foffenders need to be shipped off-
OL,10,Fisland to be placed in custody.
OL,12,FSince October 2024, there have been
OL,13,F175 crime incidents, with almost 40%
OL,14,Finvolving roads, bikes, or tractors.
OL,16,FThere have also been 17 gun incidents,
OL,17,Fnine domestic abuse cases and 14
OL,18,Freports of theft on the island.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
