PN,38304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775056271
OL,3,CUrgent calls to upgrade one of the
OL,4,Cworld's smallest working jails
OL,6,FThe offences have led the Constables
OL,7,Fto call for more robust laws to
OL,8,Fcontrol who comes in and out of the
OL,9,Fisland.
OL,11,FSark is a popular destination among
OL,12,Ftourists, attracting tens of thousands
OL,13,Fof tourists each year.
OL,15,FWhile the majority of hotels do carry
OL,16,Fout background checks on their staff,
OL,17,Fit is not a legal requirement for any
OL,18,Fbusiness to do so.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
