PN,38305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F383A1775056271
OL,3,CUrgent calls to upgrade one of the
OL,4,Cworld's smallest working jails
OL,6,FPaul Armorgie, Marketing Director of
OL,7,FSark's Stocks Hotel, told ITV News:
OL,8,F"Employers don't want to be bringing
OL,9,Fin scoundrels, ne'er-do-wells and
OL,10,Fvagabonds.
OL,12,F"They want to be sure that the people
OL,13,Fthat they are employing and working
OL,14,Fwith are appropriate; number one that
OL,15,Fthey can do the job and number two
OL,16,Fthat they can fit in to the community."
OL,18,FThe island's government - Chief Pleas
OL,19,Fof Sark - will be reviewing the
OL,20,FConstables' recommendations at the
OL,21,Fupcoming Easter meeting.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
